{"about_the_game":"<h2 class=\"bb_tag\">A hidden object roleplaying game</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Seeking Adventure is a hidden object game with a dash of roleplaying and dice rolling.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3436560/extras/Wheat-ezgif.com-optimize.gif?t=1736881886\" /> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><i>Search dozens of hand designed levels for secret loot and hidden objects.\u00a0Solve puzzles, complete quests and unlock new levels in this laid back RPG about finding stuff.</i></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3436560/extras/Quest_optimized.gif?t=1736881886\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Conquer challenges by rolling dice based on your equipped gear.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3436560/extras/Challenge_optimized.gif?t=1736881886\" /></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Features</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Attribute based stats</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Inventory and equipment system</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Complete quests to find loot</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Complete challenges by rolling dice</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Equip better gear to improve your dice rolls</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Explore a large open world filled with individual hand designed levels</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Check off objects in each level to track your completion</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p>","background":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3436560/page_bg_generated_v6b.jpg?t=1736881886","background_raw":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3436560/page_bg_generated.jpg?t=1736881886","capsule_image":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.c